    "First, comparison to any open-source LLM or non-LLM-based method may be missing.",
    "Our results (Figure 4) show that this is similarly prevalent regardless of the publication status, appearing in 71 (∼ 50%) of pre-prints and 30 (∼ 43%) of published papers.",
